{"tid":2085976,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"醫管局又跪啦","createTime":"2020-06-30T06:23:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T12:40:15.000Z","uid":84817,"like":3,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"22bf8dd1f1aa1c75124dc8d9b4ec989e771002bb","tid":2085976,"uid":84817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T06:23:23.000Z","msg":"Dear colleagues<br />\n <br />\nAs a public organization, the Hospital Authority (HA) is accountable to the community.  HA and our staff must strive to protect and uphold HA&rsquo;s and staff&rsquo;s own reputation, professionalism and integrity. In the performance of our duties and obligations, staff shall adhere to and observe all applicable HA rules and regulations including the HA Code of Conduct and human resources policies.  It is also our responsibility as staff to conform to such codes of practice relevant to our profession. When officially representing the HA, we shall be politically neutral and should be seen as such.  <br />\n <br />\nThe dress code for staff while at work is to project HA&rsquo;s corporate image as a professional health care organization. In this respect, staff&rsquo;s appearance (in uniform or not), conduct and behaviors at work, as well as the workplace should present an image of professionalism and confidence to patients, service recipients and the general public.<br />\n <br />\nStaff are strongly reminded that they should not, while at work, wear any ornaments or display in the workplace any materials that would cause mistrust or would be perceived as biased and offending by patients, service recipients, the general public or co-workers. <br />\n <br />\nWe trust colleagues will strive to ensure our services are professional and meet the standards set.  Non-compliance with the relevant HA codes, policies or guidelines will be followed up in accordance with the prevailing patient/public/staff complaint mechanisms as well as HA&rsquo;s HR policies as appropriate. <br />\n<br />\nHead Office Human Resources<br />\n______________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________<br />\n <br />\n各位同事：<br />\n <br />\n作為公營機構，醫院管理局(醫管局)須就我們的行為向社會負責。醫管局及其員工需致力保障及維護本局及員工個人的聲譽、專業精神及品格操守。員工在履行職責時，需符合相關醫管局的條例和守則包括醫管局行為守則及人力資源政策。作為員工，我們有責任遵守我們的專業行為守則。當在公務上代表醫管局時，我們需保持政治中立，同時亦保持及照顧社會的觀感。<br />\n  <br />\n員工在工作時的衣著守則是提升醫管局作為醫療專業的機構形象。因此，員工在工作時及在工作場所中，其服飾(無論是否穿著工作制服)、舉止及行為應表現專業形象，並給予病人、服務受眾及市民大眾足夠的信心。<br />\n <br />\n員工在工作時和在工作場所不應穿戴或展示任何會令人反感，或引致病人、服務受眾、市民大眾和同事不信任，或被認為可能導致有偏頗及感覺被冒犯的飾物或物件。<br />\n <br />\n我們深信同事會竭力確保醫管局專業的服務，並遵守既定準則。員工如沒有遵從醫管局行為守則、相關政策或指引，本局會根據既定的病人、公眾人士、員工投訴機制及人力資源政策作適切跟進。<br />\n<br />\n總辦事處人力資源部"},{"pid":"88aaba8d3e3128d7d1a8bce0f455325b107f4d9e","tid":2085976,"uid":166474,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T06:25:00.000Z","msg":"永不捐血, 叫藍屍伯伯捐埋我地果份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"367e600445301e43f99bca34cfbfd27c10c3dd9f","tid":2085976,"uid":53364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T06:25:05.000Z","msg":"垃撚圾"},{"pid":"4980e26b0a3c1855e19cfe2b0ee4e485cc4ba317","tid":2085976,"uid":40867,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T06:25:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n下次帶風林火山<br />\n睇下又會唔會出信<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母"},{"pid":"3b85b27917676b31ded1b8d317a13eeea40e6941","tid":2085976,"uid":11291,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T06:25:56.000Z","msg":"叫班藍絲捐囉<br />\n個個咁大隻有氣有力"},{"pid":"e89a3ba05ba9ff3f364a69b7c41c330a2e54e090","tid":2085976,"uid":268519,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T06:26:23.000