msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QH0oczb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQH0oczb.png&h=6f3fd1ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n捐血？捐你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之前都諗過係咪唔應該再捐，不過又見到紅十字會有去理大。。不過宜家唔洗再煩，以後都唔捐"},{"pid":"7b3adeb591649e3500b0f5894e7459086a09f95c","tid":2085976,"uid":82359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T06:57:45.000Z","msg":"跪乜鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本身就蛇鼠一家"},{"pid":"b377187e9e4d02897904939eb0f24e89ebb97e20","tid":2085976,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T07:51:50.000Z","msg":"等睇血庫告急<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今年七一要加主題：<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n寧願最後不得善終<br />\n也不考慮含淚折衷<br />\n<br />\n我要美國制裁，無懼與支共同歸於盡，寧死捍衛自由民主</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n認同就拎張紙舉<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Thanks, Pompeo</span></span></strong>比美國睇，咪比條廢老Martin Lee騎劫我地，搞到美國以為我地驚攬炒而唔做野<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黃世澤出左香港自治法篤灰指南，好有用，大家入去睇</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/s6o2r5DkT-w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fs6o2r5DkT-w&d=BZN1wbl1lFElyj%2BXlEN3CHHr90zhVRml9IH8Z62du0k%3D&h=28fc3281\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/s6o2r5DkT-w</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n借個位<br />\n正視聽：若抗爭方向不隨局勢改變，只會無謂地損兵折將<br />\n香港街頭抗爭目標，亦都係街頭抗爭最大效果；&ldquo;攬炒&rdquo;已經達到，今次搞蟈安法其實仲攬炒過上年出老解。<br />\n宜家<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">跟著落黎就係引導全球政府同議會（尤其美國）對付支那以及滅共</span></strong>，所以大家重點應該著眼帶出清晰民意授權比各國政府做野，畫面靚+全球廣泛報導（類似反蟈安法銅鑼灣自由行）係最理想，用選票帶出民意亦十分重要。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大家要小心五毛、熱狗放負風向：美國唔會幫我地（舊年年尾）-》英國係廢國無用架（今年年頭）-》歐盟奶共唔會幫我地、美國廢架制裁無用（宜家）</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n大家要記住，香港生路只有一條：救香港人+攬炒促進支爆+重建香港。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">沒有支爆，香港獨立或者歸英等重建方案全部都係痴人說夢。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n未來幾個月至支共瓦解期間大家要做嘅事：1.<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">走資</span></strong>2.全球救生艇<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">救手足加有細路既黃絲家庭</span></strong>（細路是重點，香港未來棟樑，正如今時今日d前線義士，咪比佢地洗腦變小糞紅，否則香港係真正玩完）3.比足夠<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">民意授權，敦促美國以至各國凌遲式消除香港作為支那獲得外資渠道</span></strong>，包括但不限於：禁止美國個人或公司投資港股，暫停接受香港用美元結算等等4.最後就真係等<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>支那自己爆</strong></span>"},{"pid":"2e845c5c829e8e3afe1b9489d88e773eb4348e42","tid":2085976,"uid":63406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e89a3ba05ba9ff3f364a69b7c41c330a2e54e090","tid":2085976,"uid":268519,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T06:26:23.000Z","msg":"蝗軍+1<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0ZDQBRE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0ZDQBRE.jpg&h=e07e5db4&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T07:55:36.000Z","msg":"真係好柒<br />\n花呢花碌"},{"pid":"16f824ed7d3ac9ce5448947632823c1cc18258f5","tid":2085976,"uid":33579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T08:06:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b461fad88ae7ba1beb5266202d4f68fea3b32b0","tid":2085976,"uid":53127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T08:24:08.000Z","msg":"即係見到條底褲黃，一係就除左佢，一係就統一要著紅底褲，唔好比人見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15f2f9252e67a70f70c26f49464f48f4d6760b21","tid":2085976,"uid":345502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e89a3ba05ba9ff3f364a69b7c41c330a2e54e090","tid":2085976,"uid":268519,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T06:26:23.000Z","msg":"